{"type":"text","timestamp":1773483922053,"sessionID":"ses_31423da25ffebo9V1CTFH0IpgT","part":{"id":"prt_cebe10887001csVeZvD8zX4H4d","sessionID":"ses_31423da25ffebo9V1CTFH0IpgT","messageID":"msg_cebe0fe50001RsYARBVuH7yrhA","type":"text","text":"Now let me work on the `tui.ts` changes. I need to:\n\n1. Add a `\"monitor\"` action type to `BrowserAction` so the browser can signal \"switch to monitor\"\n2. Wire up `onSwitchToMonitor` in `showBrowser()`\n3. Update the main loop to handle detach-and-return flow\n\nLet me first check how `TaskBrowser` handles the `onSwitchToMonitor` callback:","time":{"start":1773483922052,"end":1773483922052}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1773483922055,"sessionID":"ses_31423da25ffebo9V1CTFH0IpgT","part":{"id":"prt_cebe1101b001r3o5dpieudVYGr","sessionID":"ses_31423da25ffebo9V1CTFH0IpgT","messageID":"msg_cebe0fe50001RsYARBVuH7yrhA","type":"tool","callID":"toolu_vrtx_015BFCfSLJunLwQSCA53ZLTG","tool":"grep","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"include":"src/lib/tui-browser.ts","pattern":"onSwitchToMonitor|hasRunningWave|Tab"},"output":"Found 14 matches\n/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/wave-detach-audit/src/lib/tui-browser.ts:\n  Line 27:  *   Tab       — cycle sort field / switch to wave monitor (if wave running)\n  Line 61:   /** Called when user presses Tab to switch to wave monitor (if a wave is running) */\n  Line 62:   onSwitchToMonitor?: () => void;\n  Line 266:   private onSwitchToMonitor?: () => void;\n  Line 285:   private hasRunningWave: boolean = false;\n  Line 296:     this.onSwitchToMonitor = opts.onSwitchToMonitor;\n  Line 420:   /** Let the orchestrator tell us a wave is running (enables Tab to switch) */\n  Line 422:     this.hasRunningWave = running;\n  Line 562:     // Tab — cycle sort / switch to monitor\n  Line 564:       if (this.hasRunningWave && this.onSwitchToMonitor) {\n  Line 567:         this.onSwitchToMonitor();\n  Line 573:     // O — cycle sort order (laptop-friendly alternative when Tab is used for view switch)\n  Line 1019:     if (this.hasRunningWave) {\n  Line 1020:       line1 += `  {gray-fg}Tab{/gray-fg} monitor`;","title":"onSwitchToMonitor|hasRunningWave|Tab","metadata":{"matches":14,"truncated":false},"time":{"start":1773483922051,"end":1773483922055}}}}
