{"type":"text","timestamp":1773483931884,"sessionID":"ses_31423da25ffebo9V1CTFH0IpgT","part":{"id":"prt_cebe125ba0013Lz2uej1iTyDeZ","sessionID":"ses_31423da25ffebo9V1CTFH0IpgT","messageID":"msg_cebe11d04001KuaCIA82HNP3ai","type":"text","text":"The `TaskBrowser` already has full Tab-to-monitor support built in. It just needs `onSwitchToMonitor` to be wired up (it's currently `undefined` in `showBrowser`), and `setHasRunningWave(true)` to be called.\n\nNow let me update `tui.ts`. I need to:\n\n1. Add `\"monitor\"` to `BrowserAction` type\n2. Wire up `onSwitchToMonitor` in `showBrowser()` to resolve with `{ type: \"monitor\" }`  \n3. Call `browser.setHasRunningWave(true)` when there's a running wave\n4. Handle the `\"monitor\"` action in the main loop","time":{"start":1773483931883,"end":1773483931883}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1773483932436,"sessionID":"ses_31423da25ffebo9V1CTFH0IpgT","part":{"id":"prt_cebe1314e0015BqKqnaRanDAnj","sessionID":"ses_31423da25ffebo9V1CTFH0IpgT","messageID":"msg_cebe11d04001KuaCIA82HNP3ai","type":"tool","callID":"toolu_vrtx_018AoYGsGNJu96svtZ81y5hy","tool":"edit","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/wave-detach-audit/src/commands/tui.ts","newString":"type BrowserAction =\n  | { type: \"launch\"; ids: string[] }\n  | { type: \"errand\" }\n  | { type: \"back\" }\n  | { type: \"monitor\" }\n  | { type: \"quit\" };","oldString":"type BrowserAction =\n  | { type: \"launch\"; ids: string[] }\n  | { type: \"errand\" }\n  | { type: \"back\" }\n  | { type: \"quit\" };"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","title":"src/commands/tui.ts","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/wave-detach-audit/src/lib/tui.ts":[{"range":{"start":{"line":29,"character":0},"end":{"line":29,"character":46}},"message":"'execSync' is declared but its value is never read.","severity":4,"code":6133,"source":"typescript"}],"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wombo-combo-worktrees/wave-detach-audit/src/commands/launch.ts":[{"range":{"start":{"line":33,"character":2},"end":{"line":33,"character":19}},"message":"'areAgentDepsReady' is declared but its value is never read.","severity":4,"code":6133,"source":"typescript"},{"range":{"start":{"line":38,"character":7},"end":{"line":38,"character":29}},"message":"'SerializedSchedulePlan' is declared but its value is never read.","severity":4,"code":6133,"source":"typescript"},{"range":{"start":{"line":57,"character":2},"end":{"line":57,"character":18}},"message":"'retryInteractive' is declared but its value is never read.","severity":4,"code":6133,"source":"typescript"},{"range":{"start":{"line":78,"character":7},"end":{"line":78,"character":15}},"message":"'DepGraph' is declared but its value is never read.","severity":4,"code":6133,"sou