h (save state, stop TUI, resolve promise)","priority":"high","status":"completed"},{"content":"Wire up onSwitchToMonitor in tui.ts showBrowser() so Tab key works","priority":"high","status":"completed"},{"content":"Update tui.ts main loop to handle detach-and-return flow (re-enter browser after Q from monitor)","priority":"high","status":"completed"},{"content":"Enhance Task Browser 'running wave' indicator visibility","priority":"medium","status":"completed"},{"content":"Handle edge case: all agents finish while monitor is closed","priority":"medium","status":"in_progress"},{"content":"Handle edge case: mixed success/failure while monitor is closed","priority":"medium","status":"pending"},{"content":"Run typecheck (bun run typecheck)","priority":"high","status":"pending"},{"content":"Run build (bun run build)","priority":"high","status":"pending"},{"content":"Commit all changes with conventional commit messages","priority":"high","status":"pending"}],"truncated":false},"time":{"start":1773484075770,"end":1773484075771}}}}
