{"type":"text","timestamp":1773484237976,"sessionID":"ses_31423da25ffebo9V1CTFH0IpgT","part":{"id":"prt_cebe5ca8b002Aj7jXF1iFO4CJo","sessionID":"ses_31423da25ffebo9V1CTFH0IpgT","messageID":"msg_cebe5c1a8001CXe4VPoU400iLL","type":"text","text":"I could add a `detachOnQuit?: boolean` flag to `LaunchCommandOptions` and `ResumeCommandOptions`. When true, Q detaches. When false (default), Q kills agents and exits.\n\nLet me implement this:","time":{"start":1773484237975,"end":1773484237975}}}
